Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.27,0:03:49.98,Default,,0,0,0,,基本上都收拾掉了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.44,0:03:53.05,Default,,0,0,0,,莉雅丝小姐她们没事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.21,0:03:54.94,Default,,0,0,0,,回家吧 爱西亚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.77,0:03:58.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我们还要一起参加运动会的二人三脚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.94,0:04:01.27,Default,,0,0,0,,得去练习…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.64,0:04:02.41,Default,,0,0,0,,一诚
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.09,0:04:11.29,Default,,0,0,0,,不能饶恕 不能饶恕
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.29,0:04:14.51,Default,,0,0,0,,砍 我要砍死你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.68,0:04:20.65,Default,,0,0,0,,洁诺薇亚
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.36,0:04:24.41,Default,,0,0,0,,没用的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.28,0:04:31.15,Default,,0,0,0,,把爱西亚还我 她是我的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.60,0:04:34.98,Default,,0,0,0,,很温柔 她比任何人还要温柔…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.23,0:04:37.53,Default,,0,0,0,,可恶！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.53,0:04:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,社长 爱西亚不见了 得快点去找她
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.40,0:04:47.04,Default,,0,0,0,,她是我的…是我们重要的家人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.45,0:04:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,一诚…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.25,0:04:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的 吉蒙里的公主真是恶趣味
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.27,0:04:55.59,Default,,0,0,0,,那边的红色肮脏东西
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.59,0:04:59.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我已经把那丫头丢到次元的另一头了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.36,0:05:03.35,Default,,0,0,0,,她应该已经尸骨无存了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.90,0:05:06.28,Default,,0,0,0,,也就是说她死了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.75,0:05:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 法夫纳 陪我闹一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.70,0:05:18.89,Default,,0,0,0,,瑟杰克斯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.89,0:05:22.29,Default,,0,0,0,,你这个可恨的虚伪的存在！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.29,0:05:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,克鲁泽雷 为了让恶魔这个种族继续存活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.00,0:05:29.83,Default,,0,0,0,,现在的冥界不需要战争
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.24,0:05:35.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你这不单跟堕天使 甚至还跟天使勾结的混蛋 没资格谈论恶魔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.66,0:05:41.32,Default,,0,0,0,,你加入了祸之团这种被排斥者的俱乐部还真能说出这种话来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.96,0:05:47.70,Default,,0,0,0,,克鲁泽雷 我作为魔王 我现在要排除与冥界敌对的人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.77,0:05:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,这、这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.85,0:05:55.98,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么可能 为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.29,0:05:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.30,0:06:02.41,Default,,0,0,0,,真货要输给假货…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.01,0:06:06.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我把他连同在他体内蠢蠢欲动的蛇一并消灭了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.60,0:06:12.97,Default,,0,0,0,,没想到你自己会出场
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.46,0:06:15.61,Default,,0,0,0,,阿撒塞勒 好久不见
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.22,0:06:18.98,Default,,0,0,0,,一诚…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.79,0:06:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,莉雅丝•吉蒙里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.98,0:06:26.99,Default,,0,0,0,,赤龙帝…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.99,0:06:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,不想死就马上离开这里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.71,0:06:35.33,Default,,0,0,0,,那边的恶魔 你叫夏尔巴来着？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.60,0:06:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你搞错了选项
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.71,0:06:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,这个灵气的量和力量…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.04,0:06:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,危险
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.40,0:06:50.31,Default,,0,0,0,,一诚！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.20,0:06:54.97,Default,,0,0,0,,到底发生了什么事？一诚
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.89,0:06:57.83,Default,,0,0,0,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.49,0:07:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}吾，乃觉醒者
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.98,0:07:09.15,Default,,0,0,0,,开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.59,0:07:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,要开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.65,0:07:15.95,Default,,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.95,0:07:19.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}乃自神夺得霸之理之二天龙也
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.39,0:07:21.87,Default,,0,0,0,,一直都是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.22,0:07:26.78,Default,,0,0,0,,对呢 一直都是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.66,0:07:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}嗤笑无限 忧虑梦幻
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.93,0:07:33.77,Default,,0,0,0,,世界所寻求的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.71,0:07:36.86,Default,,0,0,0,,世界所否定的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.86,0:07:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}吾 当成赤龙之霸王
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.86,0:07:42.68,Default,,0,0,0,,一直都是力量
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.13,0:07:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,一直都是爱
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.60,0:07:49.29,Default,,0,0,0,,不论多少次都会选择将你毁灭
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.43,0:07:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}将汝沉入红莲炼狱
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.76,0:07:55.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}「霸龙」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.78,0:07:55.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\fs30}Juggernaut Drive
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.23,0:08:03.61,Default,,0,0,0,,将你就地解决的话 世界就能得到和平吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.15,0:08:06.93,Default,,0,0,0,,不可能 吾乃不败
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.93,0:08:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你明明拥有如此强大的力量 但是却对这世界毫无兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.32,0:08:15.61,Default,,0,0,0,,可你如今又是为何会成为恐怖分子首领的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.91,0:08:20.46,Default,,0,0,0,,静寂的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.24,0:08:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,想回到作为故乡的次元狭缝 获得寂静
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.81,0:08:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,仅此而已
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.26,0:08:29.59,Default,,0,0,0,,想回到次元狭缝吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.24,0:08:31.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我记得那个好像…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.50,0:08:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,原来是这样 瓦力 你的目的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.35,0:08:43.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我说瓦力 它真的在这种次元狭缝里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.38,0:08:45.11,Default,,0,0,0,,总有一天会找到的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.31,0:08:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,兵藤一诚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.00,0:08:49.87,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.25,0:08:51.62,Default,,0,0,0,,变更计划
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.93,0:08:53.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我们现在去冥界
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.18,0:08:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,突然间怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.89,0:08:56.68,Default,,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.56,0:09:04.03,Default,,0,0,0,,爱西亚
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.44,0:09:09.37,Default,,0,0,0,,一诚
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.21,0:09:29.77,Default,,0,0,0,,别开玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.74,0:09:33.77,Default,,0,0,0,,好好品尝我的制裁之光吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.80,0:09:36.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Divid
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.91,0:09:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.50,0:09:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Divid Divid Divid Divid Divid Divid Divid…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.26,0:09:46.39,Default,,0,0,0,,居然是白龙皇的光翼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.26,0:09:46.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs30\pos(703,650)}Divine Dividing
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.78,0:09:48.17,Default,,0,0,0,,那股力量…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.17,0:09:50.71,Default,,0,0,0,,一诚之前夺走的瓦利的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.71,0:09:54.42,Default,,0,0,0,,瓦利 无论在哪你都要妨碍我吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.16,0:10:11.13,Default,,0,0,0,,可恶的怪物 这就是所谓的「霸龙」吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.56,0:10:17.59,Default,,0,0,0,,加斯帕的停止能力
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.59,0:10:19.72,Default,,0,0,0,,就连我的力量也…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.05,0:10:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Boost Boost Boost Boost Boost Boost Boost Boost Boost…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.32,0:10:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,糟糕 这样下去连我们也…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.32,0:10:37.65,Default,,0,0,0,,社长 我们暂时撤退吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.35,0:10:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,一诚
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.76,0:10:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,,莉雅丝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.68,0:10:42.90,Default,,0,0,0,,社长 失礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.87,0:10:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,…Boost Boost Boost Boost Boost Boost
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.88,0:10:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,「朗基努斯击碎者」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.89,0:10:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs30\pos(640,650)}Longinus Smasher
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.57,0:10:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,可恶 红龙 白龙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.59,0:11:24.93,Default,,0,0,0,,难道我们只能袖手旁观吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.37,0:11:26.84,Default,,0,0,0,,一诚学长
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.84,0:11:30.66,Default,,0,0,0,,该怎么做 我们该怎么做才能让一诚恢复原状
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.30,0:11:33.17,Default,,0,0,0,,一诚
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.66,0:11:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,果然是「霸龙」吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.13,0:11:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,白龙皇
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.80,0:11:43.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是察觉的兵藤一诚的异变 所以过来看看而已
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.67,0:11:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,那是兵藤一诚吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.70,0:11:50.23,Default,,0,0,0,,看来变成了「半吊子」的霸龙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.06,0:11:52.75,Default,,0,0,0,,能恢复原状吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.20,0:11:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,因为是不完全状态
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.36,0:12:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,有能够变回去的情况 也有就这样继续削减生命至死为止的情况
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.83,0:12:02.09,Default,,0,0,0,,不管怎么说
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.61,0:12:05.73,Default,,0,0,0,,他那样肯定有生命危险
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.11,0:12:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,爱西亚
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.41,0:12:07.30,BackGround,,0,0,0,,爱西亚
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.96,0:12:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我们在次元狭缝中移动的时候偶然发现了这名少女
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.61,0:12:15.59,Default,,0,0,0,,运气真是棒呢 要是没被我们发现的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.59,0:12:21.21,Default,,0,0,0,,这位姐姐就会被次元狭缝的无所侵蚀 而消失了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.97,0:12:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,莉雅丝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.12,0:12:25.86,Default,,0,0,0,,只要将爱西亚平安无事的结果告诉他
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.86,0:12:28.47,Default,,0,0,0,,一诚应该就能解除那种状态了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.03,0:12:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,靠近他就会丧命的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.32,0:12:32.86,Default,,0,0,0,,不过 我是不会阻止你的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.28,0:12:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,让我去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.26,0:12:35.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我也去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.25,0:12:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我一个人去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.60,0:12:37.15,Default,,0,0,0,,社长
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.60,0:12:37.40,BackGround,,0,0,0,,莉雅丝社长
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.37,0:12:41.61,Default,,0,0,0,,一诚就由我救出来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.20,0:12:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,求求你了 请你救救一诚学长和莉雅丝社长
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.90,0:12:52.15,Default,,0,0,0,,如果是拥有白皇龙之力的你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.03,0:12:54.15,Default,,0,0,0,,求求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.38,0:13:05.46,Default,,0,0,0,,白龙皇禁手
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.38,0:13:05.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs30\pos(640,650)}Vanishing Dragon Balance Breaker
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.71,0:13:08.86,Default,,0,0,0,,你打算做什么 瓦力
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.17,0:13:11.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是去压制他的力量而已
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.05,0:13:13.47,Default,,0,0,0,,以他现在是那种状态
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.47,0:13:15.76,Default,,0,0,0,,白龙皇的光翼必须要触碰到对方的身体才能发挥效用
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.47,0:13:15.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs30\pos(287,650)}Divine Dividing
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.98,0:13:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,他现在是那种状态
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.19,0:13:22.79,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 所以需要以眼还眼 以龙还龙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.62,0:13:24.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}吾 乃觉醒者
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.95,0:13:28.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}乃遭霸之理夺取一切之二天龙也
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.76,0:13:31.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}嫉妒无限，思念梦幻
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.69,0:13:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}吾 当极白龙之霸道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.01,0:13:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}邀汝进入无垢极限！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.30,0:13:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}「霸龙」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.30,0:13:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs30\i1}Juggernaut Drive
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.85,0:14:08.27,Default,,0,0,0,,兵藤一诚 你是我的竞争对手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.80,0:14:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Divid
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.72,0:14:24.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Divid
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.44,0:14:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Divid
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.78,0:14:28.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Divid
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.71,0:14:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,一诚
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.13,0:14:36.87,Default,,0,0,0,,剩下就看你们的了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.76,0:14:40.87,Default,,0,0,0,,一诚
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.87,0:14:42.76,Default,,0,0,0,,一诚 快变回来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.72,0:14:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,一诚
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.25,0:14:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我的名字是爱西亚•阿基多
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.00,0:14:58.74,Default,,0,0,0,,请叫我爱西亚
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.74,0:14:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,,爱西亚
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.75,0:15:01.82,Default,,0,0,0,,可以交到很多朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.82,0:15:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,跟朋友一起去买花束和书籍 一起聊天
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.86,0:15:09.37,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是我的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.37,0:15:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,爱西亚
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.64,0:15:15.91,Default,,0,0,0,,即使为时不长 但是我还是交到朋友了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.91,0:15:17.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我真的感到非常幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.42,0:15:19.28,Default,,0,0,0,,不过她已经死掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.66,0:15:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,那个孩子也死掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.90,0:15:27.73,Default,,0,0,0,,戏弄不懂女生的男生真有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.35,0:15:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,只要我摆出很困扰的表情 你马上就会关心我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.08,0:15:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,但是那都是我故意演的戏
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.32,0:15:41.17,Default,,0,0,0,,你可以去死吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.28,0:15:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,,一诚 你不记得我了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.69,0:15:53.22,Default,,0,0,0,,有点奇怪 他的波动与纯粹的龙略有不同
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.89,0:15:55.59,Default,,0,0,0,,中间混杂着别的什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.10,0:15:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,你来了啊 奥菲斯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.16,0:16:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,求你了 看着我 一诚
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.14,0:16:10.29,Default,,0,0,0,,你为我流泪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.16,0:16:13.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我已经…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.64,0:16:16.02,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.28,0:16:20.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我没有保护好你…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.92,0:16:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,又一次没能保护好你…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.00,0:16:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,没错 你没保护好她
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.34,0:16:31.14,Default,,0,0,0,,那时如此 现在也是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.60,0:16:38.29,Default,,0,0,0,,一诚！！！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.65,0:16:40.09,Default,,0,0,0,,住手！！！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.17,0:16:43.06,Default,,0,0,0,,一诚
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.79,0:16:49.69,Default,,0,0,0,,社长…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.08,0:16:56.25,Default,,0,0,0,,一诚 要是你不在了的话 我也没有活下去的意义了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.25,0:17:00.87,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你无法回来的话 我和你一起消失也无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.24,0:17:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,所以…一诚…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.45,0:17:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,所以！！！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.30,0:17:22.39,Default,,0,0,0,,社长…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.77,0:17:40.02,Default,,0,0,0,,莉雅丝…社长…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.12,0:17:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你回来了 你回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.49,0:17:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,一诚 我的一诚
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.93,0:17:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,那是？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.33,0:17:55.67,Default,,0,0,0,,那中间混杂的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.80,0:18:07.67,Default,,0,0,0,,一诚
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.67,0:18:08.81,Default,,0,0,0,,一诚学长×2
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.81,0:18:09.48,Default,,0,0,0,,一诚同学
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.48,0:18:10.23,Default,,0,0,0,,一诚
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.23,0:18:11.31,Default,,0,0,0,,一诚同学
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.31,0:18:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,社长…你们…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.96,0:18:16.33,Default,,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.54,0:18:18.58,Default,,0,0,0,,爱西亚！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.60,0:18:21.55,Default,,0,0,0,,是被瓦利他们救下来的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.99,0:18:23.57,Default,,0,0,0,,只是偶然而已
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.73,0:18:26.87,Default,,0,0,0,,爱西亚 爱西亚
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.79,0:18:32.35,Default,,0,0,0,,咦？一诚先生？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.35,0:18:33.77,Default,,0,0,0,,爱西亚 太好…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.77,0:18:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,爱西亚
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.52,0:18:39.22,BackGround,,0,0,0,,爱西亚 爱西亚 爱西亚…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.96,0:18:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,洁诺薇亚同学 怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.26,0:18:39.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我好难受
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.78,0:18:43.53,Default,,0,0,0,,爱西亚 我们是朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.53,0:18:44.02,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.02,0:18:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,,永远永远都是朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.72,0:18:46.06,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.06,0:18:49.79,Default,,0,0,0,,所以 不要再丢下我一个人了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.68,0:18:54.73,Default,,0,0,0,,好的 永远都是朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.23,0:18:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,爱西亚…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.30,0:18:57.93,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.18,0:19:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,兵藤一诚
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.61,0:19:01.87,Default,,0,0,0,,好好看着
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.86,0:19:05.99,Default,,0,0,0,,那就是我想看到的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.41,0:19:13.25,Default,,0,0,0,,那是…？！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.07,0:19:15.71,Default,,0,0,0,,龙中之龙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.07,0:19:15.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs30\pos(640,650)}Dragon of Dragon
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.04,0:19:19.21,Default,,0,0,0,,人称DxD 真赤龙神帝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.95,0:19:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,伟大之红
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.95,0:19:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs30\pos(640,650)}Great Red
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.85,0:19:23.29,Default,,0,0,0,,伟大之红…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.02,0:19:25.11,Default,,0,0,0,,DxD…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.11,0:19:29.83,Default,,0,0,0,,自愿栖息在次元夹缝 永远飞翔于其中
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.69,0:19:32.76,Default,,0,0,0,,那既是奥菲斯的目的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.32,0:19:35.39,Default,,0,0,0,,也是我想打倒的目标
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.39,0:19:36.25,Default,,0,0,0,,目标？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.93,0:19:42.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我想要成为真白龙皇——白龙神皇
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.53,0:19:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,总有一天我要打倒这个伟大之红
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.47,0:19:52.45,Default,,0,0,0,,伟大之红<Great Red> 好久不见
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.28,0:19:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,你是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.40,0:19:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,刚才还不在这的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.25,0:20:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,,奥菲斯 无限龙神
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.20,0:20:00.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs30\pos(707,650)}Uroboros Dragon
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.16,0:20:02.35,Default,,0,0,0,,什么？！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.93,0:20:04.15,Default,,0,0,0,,奥菲斯就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.15,0:20:06.30,Default,,0,0,0,,祸之团的老大
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.16,0:20:11.11,Default,,0,0,0,,吾终有一天将获得静寂
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.25,0:20:17.94,Default,,0,0,0,,兵藤一诚 你想打倒我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.34,0:20:20.47,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 当然想
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.22,0:20:25.22,Default,,0,0,0,,要是社长还有朱乃姐的欧派缩小一半的话可是要出大事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.84,0:20:28.76,Default,,0,0,0,,你果然很有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.67,0:20:31.83,Default,,0,0,0,,变得更强大吧 兵藤一诚
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.32,0:20:37.75,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 回家吧 回我们的家
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.75,0:20:38.58,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.03,0:20:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,社长
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.40,0:20:46.81,Default,,0,0,0,,欢迎回来喵
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.81,0:20:48.89,Default,,0,0,0,,找到了伟大之红吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.89,0:20:50.93,Default,,0,0,0,,只是看到他的样子而已
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.93,0:20:52.57,Default,,0,0,0,,只有这样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.57,0:20:55.06,Default,,0,0,0,,还有各种其他原因嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.38,0:21:02.74,Default,,0,0,0,,卡特蕾雅 克鲁泽雷 夏尔巴
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.64,0:21:06.35,Default,,0,0,0,,既然是崇高的前魔王的血族后裔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.35,0:21:09.58,Default,,0,0,0,,那就要为这种生存的方式而骄傲
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.48,0:21:13.33,Default,,0,0,0,,话说 你帮赤龙帝的理由是什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.76,0:21:15.53,Default,,0,0,0,,真不像你的作风
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.53,0:21:16.76,Default,,0,0,0,,一时兴起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.11,0:21:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,仅此而已
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.47,0:21:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,可能一切都还没结束
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.42,0:21:28.16,Default,,0,0,0,,给我记住了 兵藤一诚
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.67,0:21:33.40,Default,,0,0,0,,社长 我好像又乱来 让你伤脑筋了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.40,0:21:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.05,0:21:38.04,Default,,0,0,0,,没有 你是最棒的…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.59,0:21:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,不 你是我最棒的仆人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.70,0:21:44.47,Default,,0,0,0,,是 我永远都是社长的…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.47,0:21:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,一诚
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.24,0:21:47.17,Default,,0,0,0,,一诚！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.78,0:21:53.34,Default,,0,0,0,,对你而言 和平也是会伴随着痛苦的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.34,0:21:55.34,Default,,0,0,0,,一诚！！！
